{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, mix modeling lacks these constraints, but it has more limited resolution.",
    "As such, the two methods complement each other and can be combined for a more holistic marketing analytics tool.",
    "We focus on how various LLMs perform, with and without refinement, on a variety of tasks that are important to deploying a marketing analytics copilot.",
    "This work contributes to the literature in two respects.",
    "First, it demonstrates how LLMs can be usedin analytics tools, with a specific focus on marketing analytics tools."
  ]
}